  						<div class="panel-body">
   							<ul class="list-group">
  								<li class="list-group-item">Based on the information from the CSIF, the ACCE/DCE decides if the site meets the needs of the academic institution. A personal site visit is then warranted by the ACCE/DCE. </li>
   							</ul>
  						</div>
					
					</div>
				</div>
				
