  						<div class="panel-body">
   							<ul class="list-group">
  								<li class="list-group-item">After both parties are in agreement, a contract must be negotiated between the academic institution and the site. </li>
  								<li class="list-group-item">Typically, academic institutions have their own contractual agreements. However, if the site requires a corporate contract, both legal departments will review the contract to ensure that all requirements for each party are met.</li>
  	 							<li class="list-group-item">Once both parties sign the contract, the site should be ready to accept a student.</li>
   							</ul>
